casebody.data:
Butler County Bar Association v. Green. Ohio State Bar Association v. Green.

[Cite as Butler Cty. Bar Assn. v. Green (1987), 31 Ohio St. 3d 602.]

(D.D. Nos. 82-6 and 82-7 Decided July 8, 1987.)

The petition for reinstatement to the practice of law of F. Harrison Green is denied. (For earlier case, see [1982], 1 Ohio St. 3d 48,1 OBR 92, 438 N.E. 2d 406.)

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
